author: NPR Music
description: The 24th annual Americana Honors & Awards show will stream live on NPR's YouTube Channel and Americana Music Association's Facebook page on September 10 at 7:30 p.m. ET / 6:30 p.m. CT. Hosted by John C Reilly, this year's show will feature a special guest performance by John Fogerty, appearances by Emmylou Harris and Daniel Lanois, and live sets from longtime favorites including Darrell Scott, Dawes, Gillian Welch & David Rawlings, I'm With Her, JD McPherson, Jesse Welles, Joe Henry, John C. Reilly, Joy Oladokun, Maggie Antone, Maggie Rose, Margo Price, McCrary Sisters, Medium Build, Nathaniel Rateliff, Noeline Hofmann and Old 97's. Presenters include Brandi Carlile, Rodney Crowell, NPR's Ann Powers and more.
title: 2025 Americana Music Honors & Awards
